 data-toc-popover-trigger=\"\"><svg role=\"progressbar\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-valuenow=\"0\" aria-valuemin=\"0\" aria-valuemax=\"1\" class=\"shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" class=\"stroke-current/25\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"11\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-dasharray=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-dashoffset=\"69.11503837897544\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" transform=\"rotate(-90 12 12)\" class=\"transition-all\"></circle></svg><span class=\"grid flex-1 *:my-auto *:row-start-1 *:col-start-1\"><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate,color]\">Catalog &amp; Inventory</span><span class=\"truncate transition-[opacity,translate] opacity-0 translate-y-full pointer-events-none\"></span></span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down shrink-0 transition-transform mx-0.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><div data-state=\"closed\" id=\"radix-_R_1av5u9flb_\" hidden=\"\" data-toc-popover-content=\"\" class=\"overflow-hidden\"></div></header></div><article id=\"nd-page\" data-full=\"false\" class=\"flex flex-col w-full max-w-[900px] mx-auto [grid-area:main] px-4 py-6 gap-4 md:px-6 md:pt-8 xl:px-8 xl:pt-14 xl:layout:[--fd-toc-width:268px]\"><h1 class=\"text-[1.75em] font-semibold\">Catalog &amp; Inventory</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-fd-muted-foreground mb-0\">Set up your services, products, memberships, vouchers, and manage stock</p><div class=\"flex flex-row gap-2 items-center border-b pb-6\"><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 [&amp;_svg]:size-3.5 [&amp;_svg]:text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy Markdown</button><button type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_9qav5u9flb_\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2 font-medium transition-colors duration-100 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-fd-ring border bg-fd-secondary text-fd-secondary-foreground hover:bg-fd-accent hover:text-fd-accent-foreground px-2 py-1.5 text-xs gap-2 data-[state=open]:bg-fd-accent data-[state=open]:text-fd-accent-foreground\">Open<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down size-3.5 text-fd-muted-foreground\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"prose flex-1\"><p>The Catalog is where you define everything your salon offers — the services your team performs, the products you sell, membership packages, gift vouchers, and your product inventory. Think of it as the foundation that powers your bookings and checkout.</p>\n<p>Click <strong>Catalog</strong> in the left menu to get started. You&#x27;ll see five tabs at the top: <strong>Services</strong>, <strong>Products</strong>, <strong>Memberships</strong>, <strong>Vouchers</strong>, and <strong>Stock Audit</strong>.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"services\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#services\" class=\"peer\">Services</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Services are the treatments your team performs — haircuts, color, manicures, massages, and so on. Every service you add here will be available to select when booking an appointment.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"adding-a-service\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#adding-a-service\" class=\"peer\">Adding a service</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Go to <strong>Catalog → Services</strong> and click <strong>Add Service</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Give the service a <strong>name</strong>, choose a <strong>category</strong> (e.g., Hair, Nails), set the <strong>duration</strong> in minutes, and enter the <strong>price</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Make sure the status is set to <strong>Active</strong> — only active services show up when booking.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</p></div></div>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"editing-or-removing-a-service\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#editing-or-removing-a-service\" class=\"peer\">Editing or removing a service</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Click the <strong>Edit</strong> icon on any service to update its details. If you want to stop a service from showing up in bookings without deleting it permanently, just toggle the status to inactive. To remove it entirely, use the <strong>Delete</strong> option.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"products\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#products\" class=\"peer\">Products</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Products are the retail or consumable items you sell or use in your salon — shampoos, styling products, skincare, and so on. NxCut tracks your stock levels automatically as products are sold.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"adding-a-product\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#adding-a-product\" class=\"peer\">Adding a product</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Go to <strong>Catalog → Products</strong> and click <strong>Add Product</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Enter the product&#x27;s <strong>name</strong>, <strong>brand</strong>, <strong>category</strong>, and <strong>supplier</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Set the <strong>price</strong> and enter your current <strong>stock quantity</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Toggle it to <strong>Active</strong> so it&#x27;s available to add during checkout.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</p></div></div>\n<p>Every time a product is sold at checkout, your stock count goes down automatically. Use the <a href=\"#stock-audit\">Stock Audit</a> tab when you want to check your physical stock against what the system shows.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"memberships\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#memberships\" class=\"peer\">Memberships</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Memberships are prepaid session packages — a client pays upfront for a bundle of appointments (for example, 10 haircuts for the price of 8). Each time they come in and use a session, it&#x27;s deducted from their balance automatically.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"creating-a-membership\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#creating-a-membership\" class=\"peer\">Creating a membership</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Go to <strong>Catalog → Memberships</strong> and click <strong>Add Membership</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Give the membership a <strong>name</strong> and choose which <strong>service</strong> it applies to.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Set the number of <strong>sessions</strong> included and the total <strong>price</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Optionally set an <strong>expiry period</strong> — for example, all sessions must be used within 12 months of purchase.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</p></div></div>\n<p>Once a client buys a membership at checkout, their session count is tracked automatically on their <a href=\"/docs/clients\">client profile</a>. Sessions are used up each time they check out using that membership.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"vouchers\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#vouchers\" class=\"peer\">Vouchers</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>Vouchers are gift cards or discount codes that clients can redeem when paying for services or products. You set the value (either a fixed amount or a percentage off), and NxCut tracks how much has been used and what&#x27;s left.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"creating-a-voucher\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#creating-a-voucher\" class=\"peer\">Creating a voucher</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Go to <strong>Catalog → Vouchers</strong> and click <strong>Add Voucher</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Give the voucher a <strong>name</strong> and choose the discount type: a <strong>fixed amount</strong> (e.g., AED 100 off) or a <strong>percentage</strong> (e.g., 20% off).</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Create a <strong>voucher code</strong> — this is what the client enters at checkout.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Optionally set an <strong>expiry date</strong> and a <strong>usage limit</strong> (e.g., can only be used once).</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>You can check a client&#x27;s remaining voucher balance and full usage history on their profile under <a href=\"/docs/clients#voucher-activity\">Clients → Voucher Activity</a>.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"stock-audit\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#stock-audit\" class=\"peer\">Stock Audit</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<p>A stock audit is how you check that your physical inventory matches what NxCut thinks you have. It&#x27;s good practice to run one regularly, especially if products are used during services as well as sold.</p>\n<p>A stock audit moves through three stages: <strong>Stock Session → Stock Entry → Stock Review</strong>. Each stage has its own status so you always know where an audit is up to.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Status</th><th>What it means</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>In Progress</td><td>The audit is open and items are being counted</td></tr><tr><td>Review</td><td>Counting is done — ready to review and confirm</td></tr><tr><td>Completed</td><td>The audit is finalised and can no longer be edited</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<hr/>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"step-1--stock-session\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#step-1--stock-session\" class=\"peer\">Step 1 — Stock Session</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<div class=\"fd-steps\"><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Go to <strong>Catalog → Stock Audit</strong> and click <strong>Start New Audit Session</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Select the products you want to include in this count.</p></div><div class=\"fd-step\"><p>Click <strong>Start</strong> to begin. The audit moves to the <strong>Stock Entry</strong> stage.</p></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"step-2--stock-entry-counting\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#step-2--stock-entry-counting\" class=\"peer\">Step 2 — Stock Entry (Counting)</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>This is where you physically count your stock. The entry screen opens in <strong>barcode mode</strong> by default — just scan a product&#x27;s barcode and NxCut will find it automatically and add 1 to its counted quantity. Each scan is saved instantly, so you don&#x27;t need to do anything extra.</p>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>Scan the same product multiple times to keep adding to its count — each scan increments the quantity by 1.</p></div></div></div>\n<p><strong>If you click Save Stock Audit before finishing:</strong></p>\n<p>A dialog will appear telling you how many products still haven&#x27;t been counted (e.g., &quot;5 products remaining&quot;). The only option here is <strong>Continue</strong> — this sends you back to finish counting before the audit can be saved.</p>\n<p><strong>If you click the X (close) button before finishing:</strong></p>\n<p>A dialog titled <strong>&quot;Uncounted products remaining&quot;</strong> will appear, asking how you&#x27;d like to handle the items you didn&#x27;t get to. You&#x27;ll have two choices:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Save uncounted as 0</strong> — records those products as having zero stock on the shelf. Use this if you genuinely checked and found nothing.</li>\n<li><strong>Sync counted to previous stock</strong> — leaves those products at whatever stock value was already in the system. Use this if you simply didn&#x27;t get around to counting them and don&#x27;t want to affect their records.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-info, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-info size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 16v-4\"></path><path d=\"M12 8h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>Not sure which to pick? If you didn&#x27;t actually check those products, choose <strong>Sync counted to previous stock</strong> — that way only the items you physically counted will be updated.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"step-3--stock-review\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#step-3--stock-review\" class=\"peer\">Step 3 — Stock Review</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Once all items are counted and saved, the audit moves to <strong>Review</strong> status. On this page you&#x27;ll see:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>An overview of every product that was counted</li>\n<li>The <strong>quantity difference</strong> between what the system expected and what you physically counted</li>\n<li>The <strong>price difference</strong> — the value impact of any discrepancies</li>\n</ul>\n<p>From here you can:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Resume editing</strong> — go back and adjust any counts before finalising</li>\n<li><strong>Complete the audit</strong> — confirm the counts are correct and lock the audit</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"flex gap-2 my-4 rounded-xl border bg-fd-card p-3 ps-1 text-sm text-fd-card-foreground shadow-md\" style=\"--callout-color:var(--color-fd-warning, var(--color-fd-muted))\"><div role=\"none\" class=\"w-0.5 bg-(--callout-color)/50 rounded-sm\"></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert size-5 -me-0.5 fill-(--callout-color) text-fd-card\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground prose-no-margin empty:hidden\"><p>Once you click <strong>Complete</strong>, the audit is finalised and cannot be edited. Make sure everything looks right before confirming.</p></div></div></div>\n<hr/>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"catalog-overview\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#catalog-overview\" class=\"peer\">Catalog overview</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Tab</th><th>What it&#x27;s for</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Services</td><td>The treatments your team performs</td></tr><tr><td>Products</td><td>Retail and consumable items, with automatic stock tracking</td></tr><tr><td>Memberships</td><td>Prepaid session bundles for specific services</td></tr><tr><td>Vouchers</td><td>Gift cards and discount codes</td></tr><tr><td>Stock Audit</td><td>Count your physical stock and spot any discrepancies</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"@container grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full\" href=\"/docs/sales\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-left -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15 18-6-6 6-6\"></path></svg><p>Sales Hub</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">View, filter, and export your full sales history — appointments, payments, memberships, vouchers, products, and tips</p></a><a class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-lg border p-4 text-sm transition-colors hover:bg-fd-accent/80 hover:text-fd-accent-foreground @max-lg:col-span-full text-end\" href=\"/docs/clients\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right -mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><p>Clients</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">Manage your client database — add, search, and view full client profiles</p></a></div></article><div id=\"nd-toc\" class=\"sticky top-(--fd-docs-row-1) h-[calc(var(--fd-docs-height)-var(--fd-docs-row-1))] flex flex-col [grid-area:toc] w-(--fd-toc-width) pt-12 pe-4 pb-2 max-xl:hidden\"><h3 id=\"toc-title\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-text-align-start size-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21 5H3\"></path><path d=\"M15 12H3\"></path><path d=\"M17 19H3\"></path></svg>On this page</h3><div class=\"relative min-h-0 text-sm ms-px overflow-auto [scrollbar-width:none] mask-[linear-gradient(to_bottom,transparent,white_16px,white_calc(100%-16px),transparent)] py-3\"><div class=\"relative\"><div data-hidden=\"true\" class=\"absolute inset-y-0 inset-s-0 bg-fd-primary w-px transition-[clip-path]\" style=\"clip-path:polygon(0 var(--fd-top), 100% var(--fd-top), 100% calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)), 0 calc(var(--fd-top) + var(--fd-height)))\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col border-s border-fd-foreground/10\"><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#services\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Services</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#adding-a-service\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Adding a service</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#editing-or-removing-a-service\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Editing or removing a service</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#products\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Products</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#adding-a-product\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Adding a product</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#memberships\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Memberships</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#creating-a-membership\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Creating a membership</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#vouchers\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Vouchers</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#creating-a-voucher\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Creating a voucher</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#stock-audit\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Stock Audit</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#step-1--stock-session\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Step 1 — Stock Session</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#step-2--stock-entry-counting\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Step 2 — Stock Entry (Counting)</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#step-3--stock-review\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-6\">Step 3 — Stock Review</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#catalog-overview\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Catalog overview</a></div></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0ivik3ip_mfgc.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><sc